com.ibasco.agql.core

Interface CredentialsStore


  • public interface CredentialsStore

    A storage for Credentials

    Note: Implementation of this interface must be thread-safe.

    Author:
    Rafael Luis Ibasco

      • get

        Credentials get(InetSocketAddress address)
        Gets a Credentials from the storage.

        Returns:

        Credentials add(InetSocketAddress address,

      • exists

        boolean exists(InetSocketAddress address)
        Checks if a Credentials is registered for the specified address. Note: This only checks for the existence of a Credentials not the validity.
        Parameters:
        address - The InetSocketAddress to check
        Returns:
        true if a Credentials is registered for the specified address.
